      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">2</infon>
        <offset>103</offset>
        <text>A widespread and complex distribution of vitamin requirements exists over the entire tree of life, with many species having evolved vitamin dependence, both within and between different lineages.
</text>
        <annotation id="T3">
          <infon key="brat-id">T3</infon>
          <infon key="type">Variable</infon>
          <infon key="brat-type">text-bound</infon>
